WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:48.080
I'm so thankful that there are so many of you who want to pray with us this late at night.

00:00:48.080 --> 00:00:55.448
Welcome and good evening, family.

00:00:55.448 --> 00:00:57.735
Good early morning to all of you.

00:00:57.735 --> 00:01:04.769
I'm going to go over some of the things the Lord showed us in this last video.

00:01:04.769 --> 00:01:20.580
I was praying over some of the correction the Lord gave me; He corrected me on how I communicate because I don't want to bring fear to you.

00:01:20.580 --> 00:01:26.173
He said, 'Brandon, don't bring fear to their hearts.

00:01:26.173 --> 00:01:28.580
Warn them and walk away from it.

00:01:28.580 --> 00:01:39.041
' You don't have to scare the elderly or the young; just present what I show you and walk away.

00:01:39.041 --> 00:01:47.680
How they handle it is between Me and them.

00:01:52.144 --> 00:01:53.760
It is about how you communicate, and I'm learning.

00:01:53.760 --> 00:02:23.280
When it comes to the plague and the things the Lord has shown me, I truly believe with all my heart that when you are in the cleft of the rock, no weapon formed against you is going to prosper.

00:02:23.280 --> 00:03:45.670
I always want to drive that home: God always provides a way of escape for the believer.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:04:16.483
He showed Joseph the seven years of plenty and the seven years of famine.

00:04:16.483 --> 00:04:20.965
He showed Noah to build the ark.

00:04:20.965 --> 00:04:25.126
He's always had a way.

00:04:25.126 --> 00:04:26.440
He's the waymaker.

00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:29.940
He will always provide the way.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:38.480
He doesn't leave His kids high and dry and say, 'Well, you know what?

00:04:38.480 --> 00:04:42.400
You're on your own, pal.

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:55.392
' He's always there saying, 'I love you and I've got a plan for your life.

00:04:55.392 --> 00:05:17.680
' That's why I try to tell you, you can't derail your life if you're seeking Jesus.

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:36.040
If your heart is seeking Him, the Bible says, 'Those that seek Me will find Me.

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:58.700
' What the devil meant for bad, God will turn around for good in your life.

00:05:58.700 --> 00:06:06.013
If you're actively pursuing Him, you will find Him.

00:06:06.013 --> 00:06:42.320
If you're being lazy and sitting on your 'blessed assurance' and not pursuing the Lord or having a relationship with Him, His hands are tied on some things, but He'll keep that nudging at your heart.

00:06:42.320 --> 00:07:07.527
My dad was telling me tonight about growing potatoes in sacks and having creative ideas for it.

00:07:07.527 --> 00:07:20.626
He said he put dirt in the sack, and one sack produces 100 pounds in a gunny sack.

00:07:20.626 --> 00:08:05.290
He said, 'Son, I'm going to be able to produce 100 pounds per sack of potatoes, and with three sacks, that'll be 300 pounds of potatoes when it's all said and done.

00:08:05.290 --> 00:08:07.258
' Dad's always thinking and prepping.

00:08:07.258 --> 00:08:18.204
It's interesting because everybody is listening to the Lord for themselves and what He's telling them to do.

00:08:18.204 --> 00:08:20.030
Is there fear in that?

00:08:20.030 --> 00:08:20.570
No.

00:08:20.570 --> 00:08:24.520
My dad's not afraid; people aren't afraid.

00:08:24.520 --> 00:08:37.840
When you're listening to the voice of the Lord, He will lead and guide you on what you're supposed to be doing.

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:46.260
Whenever He spoke to the people about turning water into wine, Mary said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

00:08:46.260 --> 00:08:49.151
' They followed His instruction.

00:08:49.151 --> 00:08:54.410
He could instruct you to do something totally different than what He's telling my dad.

00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:09.104
The Lord didn't tell me to use a gunny sack full of potatoes, but He's talking to my dad about it.

00:09:11.930 --> 00:09:12.255
I thought that was interesting.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.184
You have to follow the voice of God for what He's telling you to do.

00:09:18.184 --> 00:09:37.250
When I'm bringing up things about the end times, whether you live in New York, Oklahoma, or California, your instruction is going to be different than mine because you live in a different area or climate.

00:09:45.886 --> 00:09:46.417
You just have to follow the voice.

00:09:46.417 --> 00:09:56.263
As the major scripture for last night says, 'For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.

00:09:56.263 --> 00:10:04.560
' I believe with all my heart that you don't need a prophetic voice holding your hand.

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:09.507
His sheep will hear His voice, and a stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:15.730
You have to be His and abide in Him.

00:10:15.730 --> 00:10:23.755
'If ye abide in Me and My words remain in you, you will ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:10:23.755 --> 00:10:35.463
' There are qualifications for a relationship with God: abiding in His Word and having fellowship with Him daily.

00:10:41.616 --> 00:10:41.872
It takes practice and time.

00:10:41.872 --> 00:10:43.152
Practice His presence.

00:10:43.152 --> 00:10:47.550
Spend time with the Father every day in prayer and reading His Word.

00:10:47.550 --> 00:10:52.760
Get into the scripture and make it real to you.

00:10:53.863 --> 00:10:59.813
When it becomes rhema to you, that's whenever it will work for you.

00:10:59.813 --> 00:11:02.120
Until then, you're just parroting.

00:11:13.444 --> 00:11:17.680
You have a relationship because of intimacy with Him, not just because your pastor tells you to.

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:22.595
Everything is about intimacy with Him.

00:11:22.595 --> 00:11:30.969
If your pastor or spiritual leader dies tomorrow, do you have an intimate relationship or will it completely derail you?

00:11:36.267 --> 00:11:36.604
You must find Jesus for yourself.

00:11:36.604 --> 00:11:41.227
Your pastor can't get you there; your relative can't get you there.

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:48.302
You are the only one who will stand before the Father alone.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:00.280
I will stand before my Creator alone, and you must find Him alone.

00:12:00.280 --> 00:12:05.920
There's so much truth to the song 'I Come to the Garden Alone.

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:12.600
' When I tell you what the Lord is saying, it's not to scare you.

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:20.554
We love you, but if you're scared, I believe it's because He's trying to shake you to wake you up.

00:12:20.554 --> 00:12:26.022
On January 1, the Lord said 2026 will be the year of 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:12:26.227 --> 00:12:30.729
I am going to shake the church and its leadership.

00:12:30.729 --> 00:12:42.860
There will be people here at the beginning of the year who won't be here very long; they're about to go home.

00:12:44.370 --> 00:12:53.240
You will see great leaders in great positions not be here anymore, and their ministries will soon close down.

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:11.880
The Lord said judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:13:11.880 --> 00:13:20.235
He said there's corruption in big ministries that I'm going to deal with this year.

00:13:20.235 --> 00:13:29.600
Some will be standing behind pulpits and fall over dead right there, like Ananias and Sapphira.

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:34.560
I saw people preaching, and they went home right there.

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:42.160
The Lord said there will be mega-ministries that will no longer be here this year.

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:48.560
There will be transitions in ministries, and they'll say, 'What about my legacy?

00:13:48.560 --> 00:13:53.453
Who's going to take over after I'm gone?

00:13:53.453 --> 00:14:03.800
' I see these generals going home and new Davids rising up.

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:11.600
I see a passing of the baton coming on an even greater scale.

00:14:31.680 --> 00:14:32.171
I waited as they asked me to stay longer.

00:14:32.171 --> 00:14:40.133
But the door is coming and a passing of the baton.

00:14:50.839 --> 00:14:51.491
I see a certain general asking to stay longer.

00:14:51.491 --> 00:14:55.100
Could he stay longer?

00:15:07.811 --> 00:15:07.989
Because he told them they're coming home.

00:15:24.302 --> 00:15:24.640
And he said, "No, this time you'll see a passing of the baton.

00:15:34.265 --> 00:15:34.470
A door will open, they will walk through, and there will be a passing of the baton.

00:15:34.470 --> 00:15:37.400
It was about their legacy.

00:15:48.640 --> 00:15:48.920
The Lord said it was about legacy.

00:15:48.920 --> 00:15:54.248
They asked him, 'What will happen to my legacy?

00:16:04.770 --> 00:16:05.000
I must pray and cultivate to make sure of my legacy.

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:08.027
' And now you'll see.

00:16:08.027 --> 00:16:10.380
They've been on borrowed time.

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:27.720
This is what they said because a new generation is coming and I see a passing of the baton.

00:16:40.280 --> 00:16:40.640
They would say, 'What about the legacy of what I leave with this ministry?

00:16:40.640 --> 00:16:45.000
' I hear this in the spirit realm.

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:47.604
They'll start to go home.

00:17:12.406 --> 00:17:16.395
The Lord wouldn't let me talk about it because I saw the individual who it was and the Lord said, 'Don't you dare touch that.

00:17:16.395 --> 00:17:23.469
' And so the Lord told me to bring that up again.

00:17:23.469 --> 00:17:30.660
There will be a lot of transition coming in the days ahead.

00:17:30.660 --> 00:17:33.650
Mega ministers will soon go home.

00:17:38.703 --> 00:17:39.320
And the Lord said, 'Brandon, this is what a transition will be for 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:17:39.320 --> 00:17:47.200
You will see a shaking that will awaken to bring the bride by my side.

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:55.469
' I touched that lightly, but I want you to see this right here.

00:18:12.440 --> 00:18:12.686
This was January 23rd, 2026.

00:18:16.573 --> 00:18:18.720
I told you 1 Corinthians 5:5 was the word of the Lord for 2026.

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:22.538
A lot of people didn't want to hear that.

00:18:22.538 --> 00:18:27.415
But I said you're going to see great leaders in California fall.

00:18:33.214 --> 00:18:36.940
There will be great church shaking in California in the days ahead.

00:18:36.940 --> 00:18:43.902
A major leader of a major church in California will be shaken and things will be exposed.

00:18:43.902 --> 00:18:51.336
I said it will go all over the media, but I've not touched it.

00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:07.680
The Lord said, 'I'm shaking churches, Brandon.

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:09.165
I'm exposing corruption.

00:19:09.165 --> 00:19:17.028
' He said, 'A major TV network won't be there very much longer.

00:19:17.028 --> 00:19:20.755
They'll go down, too.

00:19:20.755 --> 00:19:24.986
' I've warned about this many times.

00:19:30.331 --> 00:19:30.857
There's corruption in TV networks, churches, and major ministries.

00:19:30.857 --> 00:19:34.270
And he said, 'Brandon, I'm cleaning house.

00:19:34.270 --> 00:19:44.340
' There will be great shaking in the church in the days ahead.

00:19:44.340 --> 00:19:56.130
Ministers that used to have huge platforms and audiences will no longer be there, just that fast.

00:19:56.130 --> 00:20:17.954
You'll see new faces rise up out of seemingly nowhere that I will put my hand on, and I will use them and bring my glory through them—not for us to hold it, but to deflect.

00:20:17.954 --> 00:20:40.080
We're just vessels: the janitors, the cooks, the children's church workers, the parking lot attendants, people who have been broken and been on the potter's wheel for such a time as this.

00:20:53.953 --> 00:20:54.187
He will use whoever says, 'Yes, here am I, Lord,' without an ego or a resume.

00:20:54.187 --> 00:20:59.143
He's done with egos and resumes.

00:20:59.143 --> 00:21:09.451
He's looking for the person who says, 'I cleaned vomit and poo for years and just wanted to yield to the Father.

00:21:14.152 --> 00:21:17.169
I was the guy pulling weeds or cleaning up dirty diapers in the parking lot to the glory of God.

00:21:17.169 --> 00:21:21.568
' That's what he is looking for right now.

00:21:21.568 --> 00:21:42.160
Not someone who says, 'I have a doctorate in theology and can out-school everyone; I have world knowledge of the Bible,' but has no character.

00:21:52.120 --> 00:21:52.520
He's looking for people with character who will not bend.

00:21:52.520 --> 00:21:56.360
You're going to see an exposing in this.

00:21:56.360 --> 00:22:00.136
This is 1 Corinthians 5:5 coming to full fruit.

00:22:00.136 --> 00:22:02.200
We're seeing things in the church.

00:22:02.360 --> 00:22:10.320
The Lord said, 'You'll see big churches, TV stations, and mega ministers on the platform who will be no more.

00:22:10.320 --> 00:22:13.160
' They'll have to resign because of buried sin.

00:22:13.420 --> 00:22:16.744
The Lord said, 'I am cleansing my house.

00:22:16.744 --> 00:22:19.009
2026 will be a year of cleansing.

00:22:19.009 --> 00:22:23.200
' Judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:22:23.200 --> 00:22:33.787
Because of this, I will also clean the world and you'll start to see the manifestations of it in 2026—politicians and more.

00:22:58.425 --> 00:22:59.000
This has been on my heart today.

00:23:09.349 --> 00:23:10.674
The Lord was talking to me about martyrs and said there will be many in the days ahead.

00:23:13.573 --> 00:23:13.920
I was bothered by this.

00:23:15.415 --> 00:23:21.608
I saw individuals I knew who are no longer here.

00:23:24.813 --> 00:23:35.834
The Lord warned me, 'Brandon, every one of my disciples except one was martyred.

00:23:35.834 --> 00:23:42.720
' He was warning about the shaking that was coming.

00:23:42.720 --> 00:23:55.526
There are things the church doesn't want to touch because they're uncomfortable.

00:23:55.526 --> 00:24:05.109
They don't want to hear when the Lord says, 'I'm out of time,' or address a church that is complacent and lukewarm.

00:24:05.109 --> 00:24:17.460
The Lord said he'd rather you be hot or cold; if you're lukewarm, he'll spew you out of his mouth.

00:24:31.100 --> 00:24:35.440
The modern church on social media doesn't want to hear that—skinny jeans, fog machines, and 30-minute sermonette with offerings to build their own kingdoms.

00:24:37.650 --> 00:24:40.511
The Lord said, 'I'm done with the way they handle money.

00:24:40.511 --> 00:24:43.213
I'm going to judge how they have manipulated things.

00:24:43.213 --> 00:24:48.187
' The Lord said, 'Never ask my people for anything publicly.

00:24:48.187 --> 00:24:50.040
Never solicit my people.

00:24:50.040 --> 00:24:57.760
If they want to give, that's between me and them.

00:24:57.760 --> 00:25:11.330
' Diana and I have set out to do that.

00:25:11.330 --> 00:25:19.573
People say, 'Brandon, I want to bless your family or help buy Bibles.

00:25:19.573 --> 00:25:25.792
' That's because God put it on their hearts.

00:25:25.792 --> 00:25:36.205
I put links in the description for those who feel led because they asked.

00:25:36.205 --> 00:25:42.105
But I've never come on here and pleaded for help to build a TV station.

00:25:42.105 --> 00:25:49.560
The Lord has put big things in my heart, but I've never asked.

00:25:49.560 --> 00:25:53.800
He has given us huge things to do.

00:26:04.440 --> 00:26:04.600
The Lord said, 'I'm done with the way church has been; it's a stench to the world's nose.

00:26:04.600 --> 00:26:11.120
' He wants people to receive the word without a bad taste in their mouths.

00:26:19.475 --> 00:26:20.600
People are upset about the prosperity message, though I believe with all my heart that God wants us blessed.

00:26:25.040 --> 00:26:27.623
Give, and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together.

00:26:36.105 --> 00:26:36.270
People get mad about it and throw rocks, and the world won't even have anything to do with the church.

00:26:36.270 --> 00:26:39.520
Then we have the great falling away that I believe with all my heart.

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:55.504
When we've prophesied and said all the things the Lord has told us to say on this channel, it was to warn you about what everybody else is talking about right now: Amanda and Joseph and all.

00:26:55.504 --> 00:27:02.440
We've been saying it for three or four years now, and I'm thankful someone else is saying it other than us.

00:27:02.440 --> 00:27:05.410
You all need to know what's coming.

00:27:05.410 --> 00:27:15.055
Thank God for Paul Begley and some of these others who are coming up saying, 'Listen: alarm, alarm, alarm.

00:27:15.055 --> 00:27:34.433
' The senators are saying it, but we don't need the senators to say it; the Lord already told us it was coming before the senators wanted to have a meeting.

00:27:49.310 --> 00:27:49.560
You heard it from the Holy Spirit first.

00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:54.375
It's not being flaky; it's being in the news now.

00:27:54.375 --> 00:27:56.680
We're not trying to pat ourselves on the back.

00:27:57.690 --> 00:28:00.817
The Lord told us to warn you as a watchman on the wall.

00:28:00.817 --> 00:28:08.120
There's a great shaking coming with a plague and financial shaking more than what you've ever known.

00:28:08.120 --> 00:28:20.034
I've said that for years because you are hard-headed, and He has to tell you repeatedly because you don't have ears to hear.

00:28:26.515 --> 00:28:26.750
It's like I was telling a pastor today on the phone as we talked.

00:28:35.160 --> 00:28:35.560
The Lord said, 'Remember when I told you the angel came to me?

00:28:35.560 --> 00:28:41.740
' An angel came with the most beautiful sapphire blue eyes—pools of blue eyes—and he said, 'Hush now.

00:28:41.740 --> 00:28:47.990
' He put his hand on my lips.

00:28:47.990 --> 00:28:52.104
This was a real man of a savior.

00:28:52.104 --> 00:28:52.520
He went, 'Hush now.

00:28:52.520 --> 00:28:54.400
They're not dead to self.

00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:56.547
They can't hear.

00:29:12.192 --> 00:29:12.384
He that has ears to hear, let him hear what the Spirit is saying.

00:29:12.384 --> 00:29:20.910
' And they don't have ears to hear; therefore, even if they heard it from you, they're not hearing it from the Holy Spirit.

00:29:20.910 --> 00:29:31.834
Because they're not hearing it from the Lord, they'll lose it all or it will destroy them.

00:29:31.834 --> 00:29:41.840
You're not accountable to make them hear it; you're accountable just to repeat what the Holy Spirit has told you to say.

00:29:41.840 --> 00:29:43.493
Remember, 'Be still, son.

00:29:43.493 --> 00:29:47.217
' That's what the Lord kept saying to me.

00:29:48.263 --> 00:29:51.445
And then the angel would say, 'Hush now.

00:29:51.445 --> 00:29:57.627
' Now, the Lord kept telling me in my heart—the angel didn't call me son.

00:29:57.627 --> 00:30:05.620
I need to make that clear because I have 'Sister Clipboard' going, 'That angel called you son?

00:30:05.620 --> 00:30:12.560
' No, the Lord said, 'Be still, son.

00:30:17.086 --> 00:30:17.297
Hush now, son.

00:30:17.297 --> 00:30:20.276
' And the angel would say, 'Hush.

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.120
Be still.

00:30:29.120 --> 00:30:39.335
' I have to make that clear because I know you have the trolls.

00:30:54.480 --> 00:31:02.920
In all that I say, the Lord shows me, in my opinion, concerning when I said, 'Watch the holly berry bush.

00:31:02.920 --> 00:31:08.500
' The berries will turn red and everybody that was standing on a rug—the stock market.

00:31:08.805 --> 00:31:15.773
I said the snow will fall when there were no leaves on the trees, and the angel said, 'Watch the winter months.

00:31:15.773 --> 00:31:17.860
' You ask, 'When?

00:31:17.860 --> 00:31:28.720
' I will not tell you the year because I am not a financial advisor, but I saw it happen in the winter months.

00:31:28.720 --> 00:31:31.600
The angel came to me and said, 'In the winter months.

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:33.630
' Brandon, please tell me.

00:31:33.860 --> 00:31:37.760
No, find Him yourself.

00:31:37.760 --> 00:31:39.300
It's not my job to spoon-feed you.

00:31:41.653 --> 00:31:50.720
I point you in the direction to pray and find Him for yourself.

00:31:50.872 --> 00:31:54.960
Then I let go of the rope and say, 'Listen, it's not my job anymore.

00:31:54.960 --> 00:31:56.793
' But I say: pray.

00:31:57.730 --> 00:32:00.360
The angel said, 'Watch the holly berry bush.

00:32:00.360 --> 00:32:01.440
' What year, Brandon?

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:03.640
What month?

00:32:03.640 --> 00:32:07.830
It's not my problem.

00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:10.430
Is that rude?

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:21.640
No, it's love because you always have people that will ride the wind of someone else's revelation and could miss it.

00:32:23.860 --> 00:32:24.080
You could be off.

00:32:26.455 --> 00:32:28.830
That is dangerous.

00:32:28.840 --> 00:32:30.460
You must find Him for yourself.

00:32:30.460 --> 00:32:36.070
Play the next clip and then let's pray tonight.

00:32:37.095 --> 00:32:39.130
This is when I first heard it—it was during the Christmas from the White House.

00:32:56.930 --> 00:33:02.510
There's a shaking in the churches.

00:33:02.747 --> 00:33:11.870
You will see a great breaking in the churches and they will come to their knees, for there is heresy and a shaking.

00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:21.280
It's a stench before Him each day.

00:33:25.240 --> 00:33:28.771
True repentance is to turn away.

00:33:33.658 --> 00:33:40.000
You're going to see that even in the highest places in the land and on TV.

00:33:40.000 --> 00:33:43.218
If you're a friend of the world, you're not a friend of Me.

00:33:43.218 --> 00:33:49.067
He said, 'Tell them: if you're a friend of the world, you're not a friend of Me.

00:33:51.120 --> 00:33:57.480
You've cleaved to the world and you've not clung to Me.

00:33:57.480 --> 00:34:00.280
' Depart from Me, I never knew you.

00:34:10.520 --> 00:34:13.560
For there are many walking in heresy.

00:34:13.560 --> 00:34:20.013
Just because you tried to walk with the president or these people, you see this heresy.

00:34:21.106 --> 00:34:21.653
It's messy.

00:34:22.869 --> 00:34:24.994
He says it's messy unto Him.

00:34:24.994 --> 00:34:26.639
It's gross, it's stinky.

00:34:26.639 --> 00:34:28.080
Too much pride.

00:34:28.080 --> 00:34:30.782
'I resist the proud.

